    "client_msg_id": "09083b90-af75-45c8-bc1c-104126652388",
    "text": "Great. Very nice set of exercises. I went through it with one of my daughters. It took 66 mins. It mentally taxed her. I think it went very well but partially because I know the common mistakes and asked the right questions when I saw her mentally make a mistake, so I diffused misunderstands fairly quickly.\n\nI think you should use red/green/blue not rgb as variable names as thats assumed knowledge. I recorded the full session with her if you want it.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1729963545.474819",
    "parent_user_id": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "blocks": [
      {
